## Map and terrain

Map 1:4000 drawn to ISSprOM2019. Produced 2024 by Alasdair Pedley EPOC, to whom we are grateful.

**Terrain mix:** Courses 1-5 are mostly urban with small areas of grass to cross. Courses 6 & 7 are mostly within the park, where it may be muddy, but also include a very short urban section where no roads need to be crossed.

## Course information

